OL,3,CEvening Standard to drop daily edition
OL,4,Cin favour of weekly newspaper
OL,6,FFewer commuters travelling through
OL,7,FLondon following the pandemic,
OL,8,Fchanging consumer behaviours, and the
OL,9,Fintroduction of wifi on parts of the
OL,10,FLondon Underground have all affected
OL,11,Fthe newspaper, it said.
OL,13,F"Therefore, we plan to consult with
OL,14,Four staff and external stakeholders to
OL,15,Freshape the business, return to
OL,16,Fprofitability and secure the long-term
OL,17,Ffuture of the number one news brand in
OL,18,FLondon," the email read.
