OL,3,CEvening Standard to drop daily edition
OL,4,Cin favour of weekly newspaper
OL,6,FThe same memo, sent by the Evening
OL,7,FStandard's chairman, Paul Kanareck,
OL,8,Fproposed introducing a weekly
OL,9,Fnewspaper to replace the daily
OL,10,Fpublication.
OL,12,FThis would be shaped by more in-depth
OL,13,Fanalysis and relevant lifestyle,
OL,14,Fsports and culture guides and news.
