OL,3,CEvening Standard to drop daily edition
OL,4,Cin favour of weekly newspaper
OL,6,F"Although this process may be
OL,7,Funsettling, our goal is to replicate
OL,8,Four previous success with our sister
OL,9,Ftitle, The Independent, which has seen
OL,10,Fenduring growth in readership and
OL,11,Fcommercial success following its own
OL,12,Fstrategic transition in 2016," Mr
OL,13,FKanareck wrote.
OL,15,FThe Evening Standard is owned by
OL,16,FEvgeny Lebedev, who is also a
OL,17,Fshareholder in The Independent and the
OL,18,Fson of oligarch Alexander Lebedev.
OL,20,FHe was appointed to the House of Lords
OL,21,Fin November 2020.
