OL,3,CEvening Standard to drop daily edition
OL,4,Cin favour of weekly newspaper
OL,6,FRival publisher Reach, which owns the
OL,7,FDaily Mirror and the Express
OL,8,Fnewspapers, earlier this year revealed
OL,9,Fplans to cut costs and reduce jobs as
OL,10,Fpart of efforts to boost its online
OL,11,Fpresence.
OL,13,FIt said it needed to evolve to meet an
OL,14,F"increasingly fast-paced, competitive
OL,15,Fand customer-focused digital world".
OL,17,FThe Evening Standard has been
OL,18,Fcontacted for comment.
